# MoJo Hackfest 2011

Roundtable is a web platform connecting news, people and ideas.

## Installation

    virtualenv env --no-site-packages
    source env/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt
    python manage.py syncdb

## Updating to the latest version.

We're not using fixtures yet. Therefore, the full update process
looks something like this: 

    git pull
    rm db/db.sqlite3
    python manage.py syncdb
    python manage.py loaddata issues/fixtures.json

## Gimme a demo

Do `python manage.py runserver` and surf to http://localhost:8000/something/discover/